					<a href="http://scifi.sparklist.com/t/7996/127160/1557/0/" style="color: #6B3092; font-family: Arial, Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; text-decoration: none;">Samsung X360 Laptop Is Phatter Than MacBook Air</a>

